      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, representing the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, showroom-quality shine without a single scratch or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is equally pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and feels brand new and all electronic components functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in top-tier shape, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no upcoming maintenance needs. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
