    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain utilizes a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example benefits from proactive subframe reinforcement and a recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain operate at peak efficiency. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical fundamentals are dialed in for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog performance profile.",
